== wapi 0.2.2 - Release 2008/10/21

- Changed license to MIT
- Add support for overriding the default formatters
- datetime objects are now formatted as per RFC2822
    in all the formatters instead of calling str() on them.
- Use a generator instead of a list in the YAML formatter.
- Fix list formatting in the YAML formatter.
- Fix a bug in the basic authentication handler which
    caused a 500 when the user provided wrong credentials.

== wapi 0.2.1 - Release 2008/09/10

- Update to the new django-oauthsp API
- Fix Decimal representation in JSON formatter

== wapi 0.2 - Released 2008/08/29
